<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>Ni Wako Mungu! TZR133</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Ni wako Mungu!
 Ni furaha kwangu,
 Ni raha kumjua mwokozi wangu.

[V2]
 Aleluya enzi ndako;
 Aleluya,Amin.
 Aleluya,enzi ndako;
 Rejea Yesu.

[V3]
 Mwana wa Mungu
 Ndiye fungu langu,
 Na moyo hufurahi kwa Yesu wangu.

[V4]
 Raha ya kweli
 Ina jina hili,
 Na aliyeshika,ana Mbingu kweli.

[V5]
 Nimeingia
 Mapendano haya,
 Nimepata uzima na Mbingu pia.

[V6]
 Nilipo chini,
 Ni mwako kazini
 Hata nije kwako uliko Mbinguni.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>133</hymn_number>
</song>